8
00:00:43,280 --> 00:00:43,920
do you think

9
00:00:44,880 --> 00:00:46,840
I'll always win?

10
00:00:52,960 --> 00:00:54,159
You've never lost.

11
00:01:02,399 --> 00:01:03,280
Ms. Xi.

12
00:01:06,000 --> 00:01:06,480
Mr...

13
00:01:07,200 --> 00:01:08,000
Mr. Yan?

14
00:01:10,079 --> 00:01:11,799
I... I didn't see that at all.

15
00:01:12,439 --> 00:01:14,640
Just what's going on
between both of them?

16
00:01:21,959 --> 00:01:24,680
What are we?

17
00:01:29,359 --> 00:01:30,159
Xi.

18
00:01:30,799 --> 00:01:31,840
All this time,

19
00:01:32,599 --> 00:01:35,159
I've always been

20
00:01:35,159 --> 00:01:36,280
a composed person.

21
00:01:38,560 --> 00:01:39,599
You're just aloof.

22
00:01:41,280 --> 00:01:41,920
What?

23
00:01:44,480 --> 00:01:46,400
Nothing. Go on.

24
00:01:49,200 --> 00:01:52,680
The only time I got worked up

25
00:01:52,959 --> 00:01:54,040
was three years ago.

26
00:01:55,959 --> 00:01:57,680
Your sudden disappearance
three years ago

27
00:01:58,239 --> 00:01:59,560
made me realize

28
00:02:00,400 --> 00:02:02,760
that your absence

29
00:02:02,760 --> 00:02:03,959
slowed down time.

30
00:02:05,959 --> 00:02:07,640
That was the very moment I realized it.

31
00:02:10,639 --> 00:02:11,280
Well, do you...

32
00:02:11,280 --> 00:02:12,800
Take your time to think about it.

33
00:02:13,800 --> 00:02:16,159
You'll decide

34
00:02:16,159 --> 00:02:17,360
what we are.

35
00:03:02,800 --> 00:03:03,599
Lie down.

36
00:03:12,159 --> 00:03:13,199
Get some good rest.

37
00:03:13,960 --> 00:03:15,000
I'll wait for your answer.

38
00:03:16,560 --> 00:03:17,360
Goodnight.

39
00:03:22,039 --> 00:03:23,560
You're acting

40
00:03:23,879 --> 00:03:26,199
like a jerk.

41
00:03:27,960 --> 00:03:28,479
If so,

42
00:03:30,000 --> 00:03:31,240
I'll leave after you fall asleep.

43
00:04:13,000 --> 00:04:15,199
(I fell asleep in
Dongfang Yan's arms last night?)

44
00:04:17,680 --> 00:04:19,279
(Although I'm without a human heart,)

45
00:04:19,560 --> 00:04:20,959
(I've always been by your side.)

46
00:04:23,800 --> 00:04:25,439
(Let me hear his heartbeat.)

47
00:04:39,600 --> 00:04:40,120
Xi.

48
00:04:41,040 --> 00:04:41,600
Morning.

49
00:04:44,600 --> 00:04:46,839
Are all domineering CEOs early risers?

50
00:04:47,639 --> 00:04:48,279
Morning.

51
00:04:49,000 --> 00:04:50,240
(Dongfang Yan...)

52
00:04:57,000 --> 00:04:57,759
What's the matter?

53
00:04:59,800 --> 00:05:01,240
Did I press on your wound?

54
00:05:01,240 --> 00:05:01,720
Yeah.

55
00:05:02,360 --> 00:05:03,160
Does it hurt?

56
00:05:03,879 --> 00:05:04,480
It does.

57
00:05:06,000 --> 00:05:07,040
I'll apply some ointment on it.

58
00:05:35,020 --> 00:05:36,160
You've had the ointment on your face.

59
00:05:56,639 --> 00:05:58,000
What are you doing?

60
00:05:58,639 --> 00:06:00,399
You've been acting strange
since you woke up.

61
00:06:01,360 --> 00:06:04,680
A B cup is said
to be a man's best asset.

62
00:06:04,759 --> 00:06:06,000
I was wondering if you have one.

63
00:06:09,040 --> 00:06:10,839
Get changed
and head down for breakfast.

64
00:06:15,680 --> 00:06:17,120
(Though I failed
to hear his heartbeat,)

65
00:06:17,120 --> 00:06:18,680
(that was indeed a B cup.)

66
