I'll do what it takes♪

83
00:07:40,300 --> 00:07:44,425
♪To bring joy into your day♪

84
00:07:46,262 --> 00:07:50,349
♪Oh, what's your soul saying?♪

85
00:07:52,600 --> 00:07:54,759
(If would be far too easy)

86
00:07:55,199 --> 00:07:56,560
