about my identity now.)

87
00:07:56,560 --> 00:07:57,625
♪Oh, is your world changing?♪

88
00:07:57,759 --> 00:07:59,399
(Yet you get to)

89
00:07:59,399 --> 00:08:01,160
(feel me at this very moment.)

90
00:08:01,200 --> 00:08:04,450
♪Oh, is your world changing?♪

91
00:08:07,350 --> 00:08:08,830
Mr. Yan. Ms. Dongfang.

92
00:08:09,879 --> 00:08:10,879
Ms. Bai is here.

93
00:08:11,839 --> 00:08:12,639
Dongfang Xi.

94
00:08:13,399 --> 00:08:15,199
Please have mercy on Ye Yunzhou.

95
00:08:15,480 --> 00:08:17,079
At least spare his life.

96
00:08:18,600 --> 00:08:20,360
Ye Yunzhou has been jailed.

97
00:08:25,079 --> 00:08:26,439
You want me to spare him?

98
00:08:26,959 --> 00:08:29,000
But did he even have mercy on me?

99
00:08:30,480 --> 00:08:32,360
But you're alright now.

100
00:08:33,000 --> 00:08:34,440
Can't you be kind for once?

101
00:08:34,720 --> 00:08:35,799
Yunzhou is now...

102
00:08:35,799 --> 00:08:36,840
Bai Zhitao.

103
00:08:37,840 --> 00:08:39,720
Your kindness
is nothing but terrifying.

104
00:08:45,440 --> 00:08:48,039
I can give up on my identity
as the adopted daughter.

105
00:08:49,080 --> 00:08:50,440
As long as I can save Yunzhou.

106
00:08:50,919 --> 00:08:51,960
Is that worth it?

107
00:08:53,440 --> 00:08:54,440
Your hands were meant

108
00:08:54,679 --> 00:08:56,840
for signing Dongfang Group's documents.

109
00:08:57,000 --> 00:08:59,399
But now you do house chores
for a man like that.

110
00:08:59,700 --> 00:09:00,240
Is that worth it?

111
00:09:00,440 --> 00:09:01,679
As long as it's him, it's all worth it.

112
00:09:03,879 --> 00:09:06,000
We've known each other
since we were young.

113
00:09:06,210 --> 00:09:07,830
We went from breaking up
to getting back together.

114
00:09:08,600 --> 00:09:09,960
It hasn't been easy for us.

115
00:09:11,039 --> 00:09:12,240
Since you met when you were young,

116
00:09:13,600 --> 00:09:15,960
he has always lingered in your heart.

117
00:09:16,399 --> 00:09:17,960
And you kept idealizing him.

118
00:09:19,159 --> 00:09:20,320
But in truth, he is no longer

119
00:09:20,320 --> 00:09:21,759
the one you once had in your heart.

120
00:09:29,679 --> 00:09:32,399
Anyway, Ye Yunzhou
poses no threat to me.

121
00:09:33,799 --> 00:09:34,919
However,

122
00:09:38,000 --> 00:09:39,159
if you get on the wrong bus,

123
00:09:39,600 --> 00:09:40,960
you can't just stay on it

124
00:09:40,960 --> 00:09:42,360
just because you've already paid.

125
00:09:42,799 --> 00:09:44,519
Sometimes,

126
00:09:44,519 --> 00:09:47,240
getting off is the best choice.

127
00:09:53,799 --> 00:09:54,679
Thank you.

128
00:09:57,200 --> 00:09:59,600
But I believe Yunzhou is the right one.

129
00:10:19,440 --> 00:10:21,399
Why haven't you finished cooking yet?

130
00:10:21,399 --> 00:10:22,600
Are you trying to starve me?

131
00:10:27,440 --> 00:10:28,639
Our family really must have

132
00:10:28,639 --> 00:10:30,480
run out of luck.

133
00:10:30,480 --> 00:10:32,000
The women your brother found

134
00:10:32,000 --> 00:10:33,399
