168
00:12:08,279 --> 00:12:10,679
Why aren't you pretending
to be badly hurt to win sympathy?

169
00:12:11,000 --> 00:12:12,960
Wasn't that your specialty
when you were little?

170
00:12:13,600 --> 00:12:14,360
On the contrary...

171
00:12:15,799 --> 00:12:17,000
